name: qnotifications
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "qnotifications" %}
{% set pypiname = "python-" + name %}
{% set version = "2.0.6" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ pypiname[0] }}/{{ pypiname }}/{{ pypiname }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 8509398452d95c5edce789bb6085ebbb571ec37fc3903102ae60b07db4f93eea

build:
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - pyqt
    - qtpy
    - pip
    - python

  run:
    - python
    - qtpy
    - pyqt

test:
  imports:
    - QNotifications

about:
  home: https://github.com/dschreij/QNotifications
  license: LGPL-3.0-or-later
  license_family: LGPL
  license_file: license
  summary: Web-style in-app notifications for PyQt4/5

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dschreij
    - smathot
smithy_version:
No azure token. Create a token and
put it in ~/.conda-smithy/azure.token
